╭───────────────────────── Agent Keybindings ──────────────────────────╮
│                                                                      │
│ GLOBAL                                                               │
│  Ctrl-e         │ Close panel                                        │
│                                                                      │
│ INSERT MODE                                                          │
│  Enter          │ Send prompt                                        │
│  Ctrl-j         │ Insert newline                                     │
│  Esc            │ Exit to normal                                     │
│  /              │ Slash commands                                     │
│  @              │ File picker                                        │
│                                                                      │
│ NORMAL MODE                                                          │
│  i/a/I/A        │ Enter insert                                       │
│  Ctrl-w h/j/k/l │ Focus pane / diff edge                             │
│  Ctrl-w v / s   │ Vertical / horizontal split                        │
│  Ctrl-w c / o   │ Close pane / only pane                             │
│  Ctrl-w H/J/K/L │ Move pane to edge                                  │
│                                                                      │
╰───────────────────────── ? or Esc to close ──────────────────────────╯